# MCP Docs Gate

- Follow `docs/agent-guides/mcp-docs-gate.md` for docs-sensitive tasks.
- Use MCP/Context7 before implementing or configuring external libraries.
- Read MCP tool schema before calling MCP tools.
- Stop and report if required docs tooling is unavailable.
- Do not continue from memory for docs-sensitive work unless the user explicitly asks.
- Keep documentation queries focused to reduce token usage.
